# MISC::GET_CONTENT_TO_LOAD

## Summary
This is used by the LiveArea on PS4

## Returns
* **STRING**

## Description
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Gets the content name to load when the game is launched.

Returns pointer to an empty string.
